data.description: Looking for that perfect ranch floor plan in Black Forest with a Pikes Peak view? This is it! Former model home built by Vantage Homes. Boasting over 4,000 square feet, 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, 3 fireplaces, central AC and a 3 car garage space that is heated and cooled. One of the garage spaces it currently utilized as an office which would make a great workshop. Situated on a sprawling 2.5 acre lot providing you the perfect blend or privacy and convenience to amenities. Zoned for horses and other animals, outbuildings and RV's, allowing you to indulge in your equestrian passions or store your recreational vehicles with ease. Located only 2 minutes from the popular, state-of-the-art 45 acre Latigo Trails Equestrian Center which offers events, horse boarding, an indoor arena, two outdoor arenas as well as an onsite restaurant and retail shops. No HOA. The expansive great room was designed for entertaining. Hardwood floors, floor to ceiling windows with views giving the space an abundance of natural light, vaulted ceilings, fireplace, hardwood floors and a walk-out to the back deck. Primary suite with a 5 piece bath, walk-in closet and a 3 sided gas fireplace. The main level features a second bedroom and office with french doors. Open kitchen with a huge wrap-around island, pantry, hardwood floors, eating nook and tons of cabinet and counter space. Formal dining space with vaulted ceilings and architectural niches. Finished walk-out lower level. The huge family room provides the perfect space for relaxation or gathering with loved ones. A wet bar adds an element of convenience, making it effortless to entertain guests. Additionally, this level offers two additional bedrooms and one bath, making it ideal for accommodating guests or extended family members. Room to grow or for storage in the unfinished space.
